- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of error correction coding. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper proposes a new approach to analyzing the finishing time. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with controlling the computation time in a distributed system. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is relevant as the paper deals with communication between nodes in a distributed system.
